attributes.Transcription: We will now disassemble a tray, a trolley from IKEA.

attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles the rolling cart. First, he approaches the top brackets. The instructor tells him to start with the wheels. The student flips the furniture and disassembles the wheels. Then he unscrews the side brackets and withdraws the trays one by one. After that, the student removes the side bars, and at last, disassembles the base frame.
